&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fairfield Park Health Centre – Treatment Room Nurse&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fairfield Park Health Centre have an opportunity for an experienced Treatment Room Nurse to join our friendly and supportive team working between 7 and 14 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will be experienced in Primary Care practice procedures and used to working in a team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience of working in a GP Practice is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a flexible, reliable and confident team player with the ability to cover holidays, sickness, winter flu clinics and some Saturday mornings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For any queries please contact Kath Burbidge Practice Manager kath.burbidge@nhs.net 01225 485500 or Kim Harman Operations Manager kim.harman@nhs.net 01225 331616.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The closing date is 22nd November 2020, with interviews on Wednesday 2nd Decemebr 2020. Please apply at the earliest opportunity as we reserve the right to close the position early. We are only able to reply to shortlisted candidates&lt;/p&gt;
